
facebook_exceptions

A Rails plugin for rendering application errors directly within Facebook.

== License

Copyright (c) 2007 Cloudburst, LLC, released under the AFL 3.0.

== Requirements

* Edge Rails

= Usage

== Installation

Run the following command in the root of your Rails app:
  script/plugin install svn://rubyforge.org/var/svn/fauna/facebook_exceptions/trunk

There is no gem version. 

= Extras

== Sample

http://blog.evanweaver.com/images/facebook_exceptions_small.png

== Troubleshooting

If the exception view only works on the first request, or only if <tt>cache_classes</tt> is set to <tt>true</tt>, make sure that ApplicationController is not marked as <tt>unloadable</tt>

== Further resources

* http://blog.evanweaver.com/pages/code#facebook_exceptions
* http://rubyforge.org/forum/forum.php?forum_id=15872

Note that facebook_exceptions is slated for eventual inclusion in RFacebook (http://rubyforge.org/projects/rfacebook/).
